e/","depth":3},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial: Opcode Histogram","href":"/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/opcode_hist/","depth":3},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial Tools","href":"/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/","depth":2},{"title":"NVBit Tutorial: Register Value Recording","href":"/others/nvbit-tutorial/tools/record_reg_vals/","depth":3},{"title":"hXDP: Efficient Software Packet Processing on FPGA NICs","href":"/others/papers/osdi20-brunella/","depth":2},{"title":"paper reading and translate","href":"/others/papers/","depth":1},{"title":"ebpf usecases analysis","href":"/others/usecases/","depth":1}]}]}},"__N_SSG":true}